data.description: Beautiful 1 story house sitting on a corner lot. It has an Open Floor plan perfect for hosting. Already Covered Back porch with fenced in backyard. This was the Model Home for the Neighborhood Built in 2020 but not lived in until early 2023.  This 4 bedroom 3 bath home has upgraded lighting through out. Come check this out today!
